title: Opie & Jim Norton OCT 21 2015 Wed.mp3
description:
Opie & Jim Norton OCT 21 2015 Wed (03:28:17)

On Today's Show:

LEA THOMPSON, BONNIE McFARLANE, TERRY GILLIAM.

The Boys talk about today being Back to the Future day. Lea Thompson joins them & they talk about more BTTF stuff & some of her other stuff. Bonnie McFarlane joins them. They bash Rich Vos a lot and then talk about her growing up in a very small town in northern Canada. Terry Gilliam joins them. They talk about his new book, art, his citizenship status, and political correctness. Dr. Ian Smith joins them. He gets beat up a lot. They talk about some health stuff and his upcoming book. Roland gets put on a two week weight loss challenge. Rich Vos calls to talk to the doctor
